snippet.title: Bunibon 2 (by Ludosity) - arcade game for android - gameplay.
snippet.description:
Thanks for every Like and Favorite! They really help!

Bounce 'em up!
Super-simple controls, challenging gameplay.

Bunibon 2 continues where the first installment left off - at insane difficulty. Then it ramps it up.

* 66 levels
* 6 bosses
* 6 special levels
* 6 highscore levels
* 66 evil levels

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ludosity.bunibon2f2p
